==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Yellowness
<hw>Yel"low*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality or
state of being yellow; <as>as, the <ex>yellowness</ex> of an
orange</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Jealousy.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I will possess him with <qex>yellowness</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yellowroot</ent>⟦br⟧
